":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"唔計猛將傳，以前拎武器好多都要靠2P大法，但咁先叫有難度同好玩，而家個d無雙系列一個掣可以轉人<br />\n<br />\n基本上無雙系列唔需要玩人多，好似真三國無雙2的人數已經好足夠，每次新作出埋阿豬阿狗的角色，根本就呃錢；戰國4的角色起碼真係精挑細選"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:46:35.000Z","msg":"真三2 好記得 <br />\n2P 玩修羅 黃巾之亂 企係樂進到守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  都係輸<br />\n難打到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"何進下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"12bac6e0a78d6f203bc64ee0825f810ffa0cf411","tid":547943,"uid":140521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"一宜都覺得戰國一個城內戰好q煩"},{"pid":"05653bbe6f6e6adac1035e0664f54ede984fc797","tid":547943,"uid":140521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12bac6e0a78d6f203bc64ee0825f810ffa0cf411","tid":547943,"uid":140521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"一宜都覺得戰國一個城內戰好q煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:50:27.000Z","msg":"一直"},{"pid":"1a6736d22c9eb15dee39963d7364646810576043","tid":547943,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"真三2 D弓兵真係唔講得笑<br />\n幾支箭就比佢地秒左"},{"pid":"71c97961051e465799976a25664cdde74fb89d5c","tid":547943,"uid":8636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"果時仲要拆爛啲弓兵塔 勁煩["},{"pid":"699d61d282f6f8546ca4a9dce421b3c706c9b4b7","tid":547943,"uid":32968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"戰一服部個幾關潛入好麻煩<br />\n真田個關長篠之戰難打到仆街"},{"pid":"4cc0caa251205cd6fc4ec5dae418d0722eb09a13","tid":547943,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699d61d282f6f8546ca4a9dce421b3c706c9b4b7","tid":547943,"uid":32968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"戰一服部個幾關潛入好麻煩<br />\n真田個關長篠之戰難打到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"刷武器專用關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609c50ef43cb527777fb73ecc2a253328337045b","tid":547943,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61892556120b354784e2d070f32366314ed43b61","tid":547943,"uid":104041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"真三國無雙2個陣要用箭先打得贏甘寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"玩高難度，食佢一嘢無雙無大半血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09c433da63b70c011584c9530188788fb032757","tid":547943,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"無雙2斬屬武，雜魚即秒，武將1hit扣1/4，打最強難度真係清場恩物<br />\n基本上有1隻斬屬角色幫手打已經易好多（試咗咁多隻，陸遜C4最好用）<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪呢集斬屬太勁，去到3就nerf咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659bd73cc5e14c846cea1ac44cf239f72337f985","tid":547943,"uid":52048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"以前好玩在有D敵將發顛 mode 你唔做下計略野係好撚難打 打極都唔入果隻<br />\n出名既唔講   入蜀打大眾臉嚴顏勁到顛<br />\n<br />\n真三二定真三三 (好似有星彩)<br />\n成都之戰 成個場都係紅色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己友基本上得你 劉禪 同 星彩"},{"pid":"02bf19c1421f1936cd48202f952effd0b7b91bc1","tid":547943,"uid":152500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"唔記得左咩版，好似都係2，3 可以用黃蓋屈死呂布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後仲可以一開波炸npc 炸到佢跌落馬，搶佢隻馬黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad2bdb61a10a8ec993dfbf571160a08894b3d31","tid":547943,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"到依家仲好記得真三二、真三四既情景<br />\n<br />\n真三二果陣好細個，自己冇機，係表哥度玩<br />\n<br />\n果陣好記得黃巾之亂入去救何進係得一條路，有其他位可以偷睇到戰況但入唔到去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果陣細個成日係個位度睇住佢死都入唔到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真三四買左ps2，護衛兵得番一個，比較深刻都係猛將傳放個升滿既護衛兵守城門，自己衝出去殺，仲要有三個將一死就玩完，好似係關羽關平同王甫，如果玩家用關羽就另一個大眾臉頂上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好記得隻兵仔奮勇殺敵一二百人之後就會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前好刺激，兩個軍團交戰會通知<br />\n<br />\n咩xx軍團與xx軍團展開交戰！<br />\n<br />\n一見到自己友其中一個團同太多人交戰就知懶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋隻game幾均真，軍團兵多、將勁就通常打得贏，兵多將廢，對兵普通、將勁，好似會俾將勁打清啲兵，之後再睇勁將得番幾多血，多血既通常殺埋廢將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果陣見盧植得番一滴血，以為佢死撚硬，點知佢冇死仲可以佢個軍團擊破兩個軍團，勁熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前真係似幾條戰線一齊進行，依家基本上時間停止咁，等玩家清場推進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}